							<div style="width: 230px; float: left; position: relative;">
								<a href="site.do?siteId=58">Maximum Likelihood Estimation of Discretely Sampled Diffusions: A Closed-Form Approximation Approach</a><br/>
								<div class="loupe">
									<a href="#abstractPaper-58" rel="abstractPaper58" title="Details of the article">
										<img alt="" src="images/icones/loupe.gif" />
