														Perignon,
													
												
											
												
											
												
													
													
													
														and
														A.
														
														Wilhelmsson,
													
													
												
											
											"The pernicious effects of contaminated data in risk management",
											
												
												
													<i>Journal of Banking and Finance</i>, 35.
													<br/>
												
												
												
											
